	<!-- message -->
	<p><blockquote><span class="smallfont">Quote:</span><hr size="1" />Originally Posted by <b>Finn</b><br /><i>So it will work on a drogmor?<br />
<br />
Seriously, I can't imagine why there isn't a way to stop casting on a mount (other than to /dismount; /duck).  It's like saying you can only wriggle your toes when you're standing up, but not on a mount.<br />
<br />
-Fin</i><hr size="1" /></blockquote>To clear this up a little, mounts were never intended to allow the effects of sitting, such as mana regen, to happen while mounted.  However, the team has decided to leave this be, given that you cannot stop casting a spell from a mount.  If we were to introduce the ability to stop casting while mounted, we would most likely remove any sitting benefits from being mounted.  <br />
<br />
Which would you rather have?  =P<br />
<br />
Brenlo</p>
	
	
	
	
	
